summary: I kind of wish there was a channel or streaming service out there that would have let a show like Andi Mack go for 7+ seasons...
question: I kind of wish there was a channel or streaming service out there that would have let a show like Andi Mack go for 7+ seasons and follow them from 7th grade through to 12th grade and maybe college. The problem is two fold, hitting the Disney upper audience as season three is plus the issue of maintaining the purity level that makes the show so great while allowing it to evolve naturally without weird elements (like everything on Freeform these days involves cults, witches and or incest)
answer: Yeah I seriously would like more shows like Andi Mack to exsist. It seems like Disney+ will be a good place for shows like this exsist

question: I'm looking under the latest fbe video and see so many ppl asking them to react to Andi Mack like wow we really out here!
answer:
Yes!!!! Please keep commenting and up-voting each other’s comments! Here are the links to fbe REACT’s two latest videos:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q-8EVqMuFtM

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ommM1czZmYw

Comment and ask for them to react to Cyrus’ coming out storyline/Andi Mack! Also tweet them @FBE and do the same! I’ve been retweeting any tweets I can find about it and liking any comments about it and I suggest you all do the same!


ALSO!!!! While you’re on YouTube, the official Disney Channel YouTube channel has uploaded multiple videos regarding the new episode, so I recommend you watch and like those videos to boost their views AND LIKE/LEAVE COMMENTS ASKING THEM TO RENEW ANDI MACK:

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zCP2zdmCBUk

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3w_z0sH0G4A

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GjNbNOaFaaw

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5u5vFck_ei8 (this is the hard of hearing PSA from last week, but it still needs more attention and is a good place to talk about why andi mack should be renewed)
